      <title>爱尔兰央行警告称，预算不得加剧通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/irish-budget-must-not-fuel-inflation-central-bank-cautions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰央行警告称，在进入预算周期之际，爱尔兰财政部一定不能煽动通胀。]]></description>
